reviewText: I had high expectations for this dvd but was very disappointed.

This was an excellent videos.  I am going to use the technique with my twin grandsons born July 31 by c-section.  They were pretty big boys, one weighing 7 lbs. 4oz. (3,28 kg) and the other at 7 lbs. 1 oz. (3.2 kg.).  Boys are thriving.

I work in early childhood education and I train practitioners who work with babies.  I am also a mom of a 15 month old girl.  This video gives great tools to parents and practitioners for baby massage and experiences that stimulate baby development.
